fields.value: Pensions & Investments Public 100 Defined Benefit Plans

dsDescriptionValue.value: Data for the top 100 public pension includes funding status, asset allocation (actual, target, and ranges), investment returns (plan and asset class), assumed rates of return, contributions, and other key plan metrics. General contact information is also included for all plans.
